00:02:10.906 --> 00:02:13.006 A:middle
so they won't even feel like
they're getting your help.

00:02:13.596 --> 00:02:16.066 A:middle
They'll just feel as though
they're experiencing your

00:02:16.066 --> 00:02:17.356 A:middle
amazing app or game.

