00:49:46.496 --> 00:49:48.786 A:middle
Now, you might think that
tapping on a star is the way

00:49:48.786 --> 00:49:50.046 A:middle
to get that information,

00:49:50.046 --> 00:49:53.046 A:middle
but that would make it a
little too easy to navigate

00:49:53.046 --> 00:49:55.206 A:middle
into the details view
- if you're going there

00:49:55.206 --> 00:49:57.356 A:middle
on accident then you'd
be getting frustrated.

00:49:58.226 --> 00:50:03.116 A:middle
So instead, the right way to
get to that information is


