X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:49:58.226 --> 00:50:03.116 A:middle
So instead, the right way to
get to that information is

00:50:03.116 --> 00:50:06.006 A:middle
by selecting a star and
then tapping that "i" button

00:50:06.006 --> 00:50:07.306 A:middle
on the right side of the screen.

00:50:07.876 --> 00:50:13.476 A:middle
